%F A042948 a(n) = 4*n - a(n-1) - 3 with a(0) = 0. - _Vincenzo Librandi_, Nov 17 2010
%F A042948 a(n) = Sum_{k>=0} A030308(n,k)*A151821(k+1). - _Philippe DelÃ©ham_, Oct 17 2011
